data.description: Lots of new in this mid-century Cape Cod.  New roof in September 2023, new HVAC in July 2020, radon system in April 2019, new water heater 2020, mitigated for lead paint in 2020 which involved new windows on the main floor and the addition of insulation.  Kitchen cabinets have been replaced and new flooring in the kitchen.  Deck boards that needed replacing have been replaced.
